Name: appdaemon
Version: 4.0.0b2
Summary: Apps for the Home Assistant home automation package.
Home-page: https://github.com/home-assistant/appdaemon.git
Author: Andrew I Cockburn
Author-email: appdaemon@acockburn.com
License: Apache License 2.0
Description: AppDaemon is a loosely coupled, multithreaded, sandboxed python execution environment with a plugin based architecture for writing automation apps for Home Assistant, MQTT and other home automation software. As of release 2.0.0 it also provides a configurable dashboard (HADashboard) suitable for wall mounted tablets.
